						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Hero-stone set up near the village chāvaḍi.</hi></p>						

						<p>This damaged stone of about the <hi rend="bold">11th century A.D.</hi> seems to record the death of a hero, in the cyclie year <hi rend="bold">Sarvajit. Polega</hi> and <hi rend="bold">Āyicha</hi> are stated to have erected the memorial slab.</p>						

